                  <td>michaeljohnson@gmail.com</td>
                </tr>
              
              </tbody>
            </table>
            <br>
            <li>
              Data Validation:

              Before uploading, double-check the accuracy and completeness of the data in your file.
              Verify that each column contains the correct type of information (e.g., names, student numbers, emails).
            </li>

            <li>
              Single Sheet Requirement:

              Make sure that your Excel file contains only one sheet.
              The data to be uploaded should be located on the first sheet of the Excel file.
            </li>
          </ol>
          </p>
        </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <div class="container text-center pt-1">
            <label for="file" class="form-label">Upload excel or csv file: </label>
          </div>

        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-8">
          <input type="file" class="form-control" id="file" name="file" accept=".xlsx, .xls, .csv" required>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row my-3">
        <div class="col-sm-12 container text-end">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>

  </div>

